xperience and a commitment to staying ahead of the curve. We blend innovative technology with strategic insights to deliver unparalleled security. Trust SecureGuard to be your vigilant partner in the digital world.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Free Consultation</a>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SecureGuard Cybersecurity. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}